rom OT  for the selected days) <br>- *Click on  Exempt Dates for the selected employee(s) .(These employees will be exempted from OT for the selected dates) <br>- Click on Exempt Days and Dates (the selected employees will be exempted from OT for both OT Dates and Days) <br>- Click on Unexempt select Record [The selected employees will not be exempted from OT (They will be paid OT)] <br><br>Other features are: <br>- Click on the Print Report button to print hard copy of the displayed record(s). <br>- \tClick on the Excel button to export the record(s) as a report sheet to Microsoft Excel format.";
